\contentsline {table}{\numberline {5.4}{\ignorespaces Speedup relative to linear search. Higher is better. The Ajtai method achieves 3.5--5.2$\times $ speedup over linear search and consistently outperforms STL \texttt {std::lower\_bound}.}}{75}{}%
